===================== INSTALLATION OF FIGURE LIBRARY =====================

1. Possibility (ADVISED):
To install the Figure library correctly with CMake follow these steps:
(Make sure you have CMake installed!)

   $ mkdir build
   $ cd build
   $ cmake ..
   $ sudo make install

You're done now! Ignore the rest of this file.

2. Possibility:
